      "seed": 2056590586,
      "version": 313,
      "versionNonce": 1510883558,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1783354389490,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "\"Service Oriented Architecture (SOA)\" \n\n\nMonolith - a big honking application that is all\nin the same source code repository - all the developers\nwork on that together.\n\nAlmost everything is \"early bound\" - the compiler can check everthing",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "\"Service Oriented Architecture (SOA)\" \n\n\nMonolith - a big honking application that is all\nin the same source code repository - all the developers\nwork on that together.\n\nAlmost everything is \"early bound\" - the compiler can check everthing",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
